### 1. Add "Dependency Injection" Section

```markdown
## Dependency Injection with Hilt

### Overview
All dependencies are managed by Hilt (Dagger). NO singletons with getInstance() pattern.

### Architecture Layers

```
UI Layer (Fragments/Activities)
  ↓ @Inject / @HiltViewModel
ViewModels
  ↓ @Inject constructor
UseCases
  ↓ @Inject constructor
Repository Interface (domain layer)
  ↓ @Inject constructor (impl in data layer)
Data Sources + Managers
  ↓ @Inject constructor
Room, Retrofit, SharedPreferences
```

### Hilt Modules

**DataModule** (`di/DataModule.kt`)
- Provides: ContentRepository interface → impl
- Provides: Data sources (MovieLocalDataSource, etc.)
- Provides: API service (XtreamApiService)

**ManagerModule** (`di/ManagerModule.kt`)
- Provides: AppDatabase
- Provides: SourceManager, PreferencesManager, CredentialsManager
- Provides: SyncPreferencesManager, ReactiveUpdateManager

### Common Patterns

#### ViewModels
```kotlin
@HiltViewModel
class MoviesViewModel @Inject constructor(
    private val observeMoviesUseCase: ObserveMoviesUseCase,
    private val refreshMoviesUseCase: RefreshMoviesUseCase,
    private val repository: ContentRepository,
) : ViewModel() { ... }
```

#### UseCases
```kotlin
class ObserveMoviesUseCase @Inject constructor(
    private val repository: ContentRepository
) { ... }
```

#### Repository Implementation
```kotlin
class ContentRepositoryImpl @Inject constructor(
    @ApplicationContext private val context: Context,
    private val database: AppDatabase,
    private val sourceManager: SourceManager,
    // ... all dependencies explicit
) : ContentRepository { ... }
```

#### Activities/Fragments
```kotlin
@AndroidEntryPoint
class SettingsActivity : AppCompatActivity() {
    @Inject lateinit var preferencesManager: PreferencesManager
    @Inject lateinit var repository: ContentRepository

    override fun onCreate(savedInstanceState: Bundle?) {
        super.onCreate(savedInstanceState)
        // Fields already injected, use directly
    }
}
```

#### Workers
```kotlin
@HiltWorker
class BackgroundSyncWorker @AssistedInject constructor(
    @Assisted context: Context,
    @Assisted params: WorkerParameters,
    private val repository: ContentRepository,
) : CoroutineWorker(context, params) { ... }
```

### Application Setup
```kotlin
@HiltAndroidApp
class Cactuvi : Application(), Configuration.Provider {
    @Inject lateinit var workerFactory: HiltWorkerFactory

    override fun getWorkManagerConfiguration(): Configuration {
        return Configuration.Builder()
            .setWorkerFactory(workerFactory)
            .build()
    }
}
```
