- SourceManager.getInstance(context) -> use injected sourceManager
- PreferencesManager.getInstance(context) -> use injected preferencesManager
- CredentialsManager.getInstance(context) -> use injected credentialsManager
- SyncPreferencesManager.getInstance(context) -> use injected syncPreferencesManager

### 3. Update getInstance() companion for backward compat
Keep getInstance() but make it construct using getInstance() calls internally.

